The Proposal:
Shubham Multipurpose Educational Institute, Nagpur run by Dr. Marya English Convent, Kharbi Road, Nagpur
According to Sati of G. Nagpur, an English medium self-financing primary school (Classes 1 to 5).
Transfer of Management to Mata Multipurpose Institute of Education, Ramna Maroti Nagar Nagpur
The proposal received under the reference letter was under the consideration of the government.
The government's decision:
The school is managed by Sati Anusaya Mata Multipurpose Educational Institute, Ramana Maroti Nagar, Nagpur.
The Government has decided to approve the transfer to the Institute on the following terms and conditions: -
(1) The condition of minimum marks of the school where the management has changed shall be relaxed for any reason.
No.
(2) In the case of a school where the management has changed, any of the terms and conditions of the Government permission / approval
Care should be taken to ensure that there are no changes.
(3) Since the school is on the self-financing principle of English medium, the working teachers / non-teachers
The entire responsibility of the staff will rest with the organization that accepts the management transfer.
(4) From time to time, in respect of schools, teachers / non-teaching staff, salary / non-salary grants, students, etc. by the Government.
The new body will be bound to comply with the prescribed Acts, Rules, Orders, etc.
(5) These Management Changes, Government Decisions, Department of School Education and Sports, No: Mashah 2011 / (210/11)
MASHI-3 shall come into force in accordance with the rules and procedures prescribed on 17th February, 2012.
(6) Fresh complaints to the Government or to the field officers of the Education Department regarding this change of management.
if it is received or noticed that a breach of the terms and conditions regarding the change of management has occurred, or
